{"tid":2286574,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村拓哉狂被嫌老！78歲岳母曝光　超辣身材「根本少女」","createTime":"2020-11-15T06:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T08:15:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"70ab2c79a45e1ab792bfbf4de6aec398de21a3c5","tid":2286574,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"日劇男神木村拓哉出道30年，年輕時俊美五官及瀟灑帥氣的氣質，成為日本花美男代表，在全球擁有大批粉絲，不過今年47歲的他，近來頻被指出顏值劣化、男神味道不再，倒是她的岳母，也就是工藤靜香的母親，年近80還維持如少女般的曼妙身材，令人驚嘆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/12/2877172-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F12%2F2877172-PH.jpg&h=1433337d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲木村拓哉近來頻被嫌老，還被指撞臉吳宗憲。（圖／翻攝自木村拓哉IG）<br />\n<br />\n木村拓哉和工藤靜香結婚20年，育有2個寶貝女兒，相較木村拓哉近來頻被嫌老，今年已經50歲的工藤靜香，雖然臉上皺紋藏不住，但身材卻依舊苗條，去年曾曬出比基尼辣照，小麥色的緊緻肌膚、修長美腿及蠻腰，絲毫不見一絲贅肉，乍看還以為是女兒木村光希，而她先前也曬出和媽媽的同框照，78歲高齡的母親同樣擁有完美身材比例，纖瘦背影宛如少女，讓網友驚呼：「身材果然跟基因有關！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/08/27/2097950-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2F2097950-PH.jpg&h=bbebc651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼工藤靜香年過半百仍維持曼妙身材。（圖／翻攝自工藤靜香IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/08/27/2097951-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2F2097951-PH.jpg&h=7a651991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，工藤靜香曾大方公開自己維持身材的祕訣，除了維持運動習慣外，她也非常喜歡自己下廚，能夠自由控制熱量，飲食以清淡為主，且她每天都堅持吃納豆，不僅能幫助身材的維持，還能夠降血脂、抗衰老，讓皮膚變得水潤有彈性，為了身材下足工夫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/14/2881657-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F14%2F2881657-PH.jpg&h=c5ba84c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼工藤靜香媽媽（圖左）身材宛如少女。（圖／翻攝自工藤靜香IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/14/2881658-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F14%2F2881658-PH.jpg&h=56427006&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"554278b1f824b2b4db73a02a3d79c805357e0032","tid":2286574,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:20:57.000Z","msg":"樓主食得咁偏⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a6d5fd2cf7f17cdb2b83b58c813c7bf008962c","tid":2286574,"uid":181319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"她每天都堅持吃納豆，不僅能幫助身材的維持，還能夠降血脂、抗衰老，讓皮膚變得水潤有彈性<br />\n<br />\n水潤有彈性⋯⋯"},{"pid":"921ca4325cb34b713c60f277fb2d82d0c1ef05eb","tid":2286574,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"嘩痴咗孖筋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9775fe9077be050c070e6677efa6a0ed4db66836","tid":2286574,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"正呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f53d773b361cd9e297b6789f9ea97bed6aec158","tid":2286574,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21a6d5fd2cf7f17cdb2b83b58c813c7bf008962c","tid":2286574,"uid":181319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"她每天都堅持吃納豆，不僅能幫助身材的維持，還能夠降血脂、抗衰老，讓皮膚變得水潤有彈性<br />\n<br />\n水潤有彈性⋯⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"納豆不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c442ef3e0c4fb65f64a995bd4195ca6d4842112","tid":2286574,"uid":21634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"塊閪應該仲好多水"},{"pid":"267d7e4fa7dbee81928831acc5e95f512e8ce30e","tid":2286574,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":